Grammar cs2.y

    1 $accept: compilation_unit EOF

    2 compilation_unit: extern_alias_directivesopt using_directivesopt 
                            attributesopt namespace_member_declarationsopt

    3 namespace_name: namespace_or_type_name

    4 type_name: namespace_or_type_name

    5 namespace_or_type_name: IDENTIFIER type_argument_list
    6                       | IDENTIFIER
    7                       | qualified_alias_member
    8                       | namespace_or_type_name '.' IDENTIFIER 
                                  type_argument_listopt

    9 type: type_name
   10     | value_type
   11     | reference_type

   12 value_type: struct_type

   13 struct_type: simple_type
   14            | nullable_type

   15 simple_type: numeric_type
   16            | BOOL

   17 numeric_type: integral_type
   18             | floating_point_type
   19             | DECIMAL

   20 integral_type: SBYTE
   21              | BYTE
   22              | SHORT
   23              | USHORT
   24              | INT
   25              | UINT
   26              | LONG
   27              | ULONG
   28              | CHAR

   29 floating_point_type: FLOAT
   30                    | DOUBLE

   31 nullable_type: non_nullable_value_type '?'

   32 non_nullable_value_type: type_name
   33                        | simple_type

   34 reference_type: class_type
   35               | array_type

   36 class_type: type_name OBJECT
   37           | STRING

   38 variable_reference: expression

   39 argument_list: argument
   40              | argument_list ',' argument

   41 argument: expression
   42         | REF variable_reference
   43         | OUT variable_reference

   44 primary_expression: array_creation_expression
   45                   | primary_no_array_creation_expression

   46 primary_no_array_creation_expression: literal
   47                                     | simple_name
   48                                     | parenthesized_expression
   49                                     | member_access
   50                                     | invocation_expression
   51                                     | element_access
   52                                     | this_access
   53                                     | base_access
   54                                     | post_increment_expression
   55                                     | post_decrement_expression
   56                                     | object_creation_expression
   57                                     | typeof_expression
   58                                     | checked_expression
   59                                     | unchecked_expression
   60                                     | default_value_expression
   61                                     | anonymous_method_expression

   62 simple_name: IDENTIFIER type_argument_listopt

   63 parenthesized_expression: '(' expression ')'

   64 member_access: primary_expression '.' IDENTIFIER 
                         type_argument_listopt
   65              | predefined_type '.' IDENTIFIER type_argument_listopt
   66              | qualified_alias_member '.' IDENTIFIER 
                         type_argument_listopt

   67 predefined_type: BOOL
   68                | DECIMAL
   69                | DOUBLE
   70                | FLOAT
   71                | OBJECT
   72                | STRING
   73                | integral_type

   74 invocation_expression: primary_expression '(' argument_listopt ')'

   75 element_access: primary_no_array_creation_expression '[' 
                          expression_list ']'

   76 expression_list: expression
   77                | expression_list ',' expression

   78 this_access: THIS

   79 base_access: BASE '.' IDENTIFIER type_argument_listopt
   80            | BASE '[' expression_list ']'

   81 post_increment_expression: primary_expression PLUS_PLUS

   82 post_decrement_expression: primary_expression MINUS_MINUS

   83 object_creation_expression: NEW type '(' argument_listopt ')'

   84 array_creation_expression: NEW non_array_type '[' expression_list ']' 
                                     rank_specifiersopt array_initializeropt
   85                          | NEW array_type array_initializer

   86 typeof_expression: TYPEOF '(' type ')'
   87                  | TYPEOF '(' unbound_type_name ')'
   88                  | TYPEOF '(' VOID ')'

   89 unbound_type_name: IDENTIFIER generic_dimension_specifier
   90                  | IDENTIFIER SEMI_SEMI IDENTIFIER 
                             generic_dimension_specifier
   91                  | unbound_type_name '.' IDENTIFIER 
                             generic_dimension_specifier

   92 generic_dimension_specifier: '<' commasopt '>'

   93 commas: ','
   94       | commas ','

   95 checked_expression: CHECKED '(' expression ')'

   96 unchecked_expression: UNCHECKED '(' expression ')'

   97 default_value_expression: DEFAULT '(' type ')'

   98 anonymous_method_expression: DELEGATE anonymous_method_signatureopt 
                                       block

   99 anonymous_method_signature: '(' anonymous_method_parameter_listopt 
                                      ')'

  100 anonymous_method_parameter_list: anonymous_method_parameter
  101                                | anonymous_method_parameter_list ',' 
                                           anonymous_method_parameter

  102 anonymous_method_parameter: parameter_modifieropt type IDENTIFIER

  103 unary_expression: primary_expression
  104                 | '+' unary_expression
  105                 | '-' unary_expression
  106                 | '!' unary_expression
  107                 | '~' unary_expression
  108                 | pre_increment_expression
  109                 | pre_decrement_expression
  110                 | cast_expression

  111 pre_increment_expression: PLUS_PLUS unary_expression

  112 pre_decrement_expression: MINUS_MINUS unary_expression

  113 cast_expression: '(' type ')' unary_expression

  114 multiplicative_expression: unary_expression
  115                          | multiplicative_expression '*' 
                                     unary_expression
  116                          | multiplicative_expression '/' 
                                     unary_expression
  117                          | multiplicative_expression '%' 
                                     unary_expression

  118 additive_expression: multiplicative_expression
  119                    | additive_expression '+' 
                               multiplicative_expression
  120                    | additive_expression '-' 
                               multiplicative_expression

  121 shift_expression: additive_expression
  122                 | shift_expression LT_LT additive_expression
  123                 | shift_expression RIGHT_SHIFT additive_expression

  124 relational_expression: shift_expression
  125                      | relational_expression '<' shift_expression
  126                      | relational_expression '>' shift_expression
  127                      | relational_expression LE shift_expression
  128                      | relational_expression GE shift_expression
  129                      | relational_expression IS type
  130                      | relational_expression AS type

  131 equality_expression: relational_expression
  132                    | equality_expression EQ_EQ relational_expression
  133                    | equality_expression NE relational_expression

  134 and_expression: equality_expression
  135               | and_expression '&' equality_expression

  136 exclusive_or_expression: and_expression
  137                        | exclusive_or_expression '^' and_expression

  138 inclusive_or_expression: exclusive_or_expression
  139                        | inclusive_or_expression '|' 
                                   exclusive_or_expression

  140 conditional_and_expression: inclusive_or_expression
  141                           | conditional_and_expression AMP_AMP 
                                      inclusive_or_expression

  142 conditional_or_expression: conditional_and_expression
  143                          | conditional_or_expression BAR_BAR 
                                     conditional_and_expression

  144 null_coalescing_expression: conditional_or_expression
  145                           | conditional_or_expression QM_QM 
                                      null_coalescing_expression

  146 conditional_expression: null_coalescing_expression
  147                       | null_coalescing_expression '?' expression ':' 
                                  expression

  148 assignment: unary_expression assignment_operator expression

  149 assignment_operator: '='
  150                    | PLUS_EQ
  151                    | MINUS_EQ
  152                    | STAR_EQ
  153                    | SLASH_EQ
  154                    | PERCENT_EQ
  155                    | AMP_EQ
  156                    | BAR_EQ
  157                    | CARET_EQ
  158                    | LT_LT_EQ
  159                    | RIGHT_SHIFT_ASSIGNMENT

  160 expression: conditional_expression
  161           | assignment

  162 constant_expression: expression

  163 boolean_expression: expression

  164 statement: labeled_statement
  165          | declaration_statement
  166          | embedded_statement

  167 embedded_statement: block
  168                   | empty_statement
  169                   | expression_statement
  170                   | selection_statement
  171                   | iteration_statement
  172                   | jump_statement
  173                   | try_statement
  174                   | checked_statement
  175                   | unchecked_statement
  176                   | lock_statement
  177                   | using_statement
  178                   | yield_statement

  179 block: '{' statement_listopt '}'

  180 statement_list: statement
  181               | statement_list statement

  182 empty_statement: ';'

  183 labeled_statement: IDENTIFIER ':' statement

  184 declaration_statement: local_variable_declaration ';'
  185                      | local_constant_declaration ';'

  186 local_variable_declaration: type local_variable_declarators

  187 local_variable_declarators: local_variable_declarator
  188                           | local_variable_declarators ',' 
                                      local_variable_declarator

  189 local_variable_declarator: IDENTIFIER
  190                          | IDENTIFIER '=' local_variable_initializer

  191 local_variable_initializer: expression
  192                           | array_initializer

  193 local_constant_declaration: CONST type constant_declarators_loc

  194 constant_declarators_loc: constant_declarator_loc
  195                         | constant_declarators_loc ',' 
                                    constant_declarator_loc

  196 constant_declarator_loc: IDENTIFIER '=' constant_expression

  197 expression_statement: statement_expression ';'

  198 statement_expression: invocation_expression
  199                     | object_creation_expression
  200                     | assignment
  201                     | post_increment_expression
  202                     | post_decrement_expression
  203                     | pre_increment_expression
  204                     | pre_decrement_expression

  205 selection_statement: if_statement
  206                    | switch_statement

  207 if_statement: IF '(' boolean_expression ')' embedded_statement
  208             | IF '(' boolean_expression ')' embedded_statement ELSE 
                        embedded_statement

  209 switch_statement: SWITCH '(' expression ')' switch_block

  210 switch_block: '{' switch_sectionsopt '}'

  211 switch_sections: switch_section
  212                | switch_sections switch_section

  213 switch_section: switch_labels statement_list

  214 switch_labels: switch_label
  215              | switch_labels switch_label

  216 switch_label: CASE constant_expression ':'
  217             | DEFAULT ':'

  218 iteration_statement: while_statement
  219                    | do_statement
  220                    | for_statement
  221                    | foreach_statement

  222 while_statement: WHILE '(' boolean_expression ')' embedded_statement

  223 do_statement: DO embedded_statement WHILE '(' boolean_expression ')' 
                        ';'

  224 for_statement: FOR '(' for_initializeropt ';' for_conditionopt ';' 
                         for_iteratoropt ')' embedded_statement

  225 for_initializer: local_variable_declaration
  226                | statement_expression_list

  227 for_condition: boolean_expression

  228 for_iterator: statement_expression_list

  229 statement_expression_list: statement_expression
  230                          | statement_expression_list ',' 
                                     statement_expression

  231 foreach_statement: FOREACH '(' type IDENTIFIER IN expression ')' 
                             embedded_statement

  232 jump_statement: break_statement
  233               | continue_statement
  234               | goto_statement
  235               | return_statement
  236               | throw_statement

  237 break_statement: BREAK ';'

  238 continue_statement: CONTINUE ';'

  239 goto_statement: GOTO IDENTIFIER ';'
  240               | GOTO CASE constant_expression ';'
  241               | GOTO DEFAULT ';'

  242 return_statement: RETURN expressionopt ';'

  243 throw_statement: THROW expressionopt ';'

  244 try_statement: TRY block catch_clauses
  245              | TRY block catch_clausesopt finally_clause

  246 catch_clauses: specific_catch_clauses
  247              | specific_catch_clausesopt general_catch_clause

  248 specific_catch_clauses: specific_catch_clause
  249                       | specific_catch_clauses specific_catch_clause

  250 specific_catch_clause: CATCH '(' class_type identifieropt ')' block

  251 general_catch_clause: CATCH block

  252 finally_clause: FINALLY block

  253 checked_statement: CHECKED block

  254 unchecked_statement: UNCHECKED block

  255 lock_statement: LOCK '(' expression ')' embedded_statement

  256 using_statement: USING '(' resource_acquisition ')' 
                           embedded_statement

  257 resource_acquisition: local_variable_declaration
  258                     | expression

  259 yield_statement: YIELD RETURN expression ';'
  260                | YIELD BREAK ';'

  261 namespace_declaration: NAMESPACE qualified_identifier namespace_body 
                                 SemicolonOpt

  262 qualified_identifier: IDENTIFIER
  263                     | qualified_identifier '.' IDENTIFIER

  264 namespace_body: '{' extern_alias_directivesopt using_directivesopt 
                          namespace_member_declarationsopt '}'

  265 extern_alias_directives: extern_alias_directive
  266                        | extern_alias_directives 
                                   extern_alias_directive

  267 extern_alias_directive: EXTERN ALIAS IDENTIFIER ';'

  268 using_directives: using_directive
  269                 | using_directives using_directive

  270 using_directive: using_alias_directive
  271                | using_namespace_directive

  272 using_alias_directive: USING IDENTIFIER '=' namespace_or_type_name 
                                 ';'

  273 using_namespace_directive: USING namespace_name ';'

  274 namespace_member_declarations: namespace_member_declaration
  275                              | namespace_member_declarations 
                                         namespace_member_declaration

  276 namespace_member_declaration: namespace_declaration
  277                             | type_declaration

  278 type_declaration: class_declaration
  279                 | struct_declaration
  280                 | interface_declaration
  281                 | enum_declaration
  282                 | delegate_declaration

  283 qualified_alias_member: IDENTIFIER SEMI_SEMI IDENTIFIER 
                                  type_argument_listopt

  284 modifiers_opt: /* empty */
  285              | modifiers

  286 modifiers: modifier
  287          | modifiers modifier

  288 modifier: NEW
  289         | PARTIAL
  290         | PUBLIC
  291         | PROTECTED
  292         | INTERNAL
  293         | PRIVATE
  294         | STATIC
  295         | VIRTUAL
  296         | SEALED
  297         | OVERRIDE
  298         | ABSTRACT
  299         | EXTERN

  300 class_declaration: attributesopt modifiers_opt CLASS IDENTIFIER 
                             type_parameter_listopt class_baseopt 
                             type_parameter_constraints_clausesopt class_body 
                             SemicolonOpt

  301 class_base: type_name_list

  302 type_name_list: ':' type_name
  303               | type_name_list ',' type_name

  304 class_body: '{' class_member_declarationsopt '}'

  305 class_member_declarations: class_member_declaration
  306                          | class_member_declarations 
                                     class_member_declaration

  307 class_member_declaration: constant_declaration
  308                         | field_declaration
  309                         | method_declaration
  310                         | property_declaration
  311                         | event_declaration
  312                         | indexer_declaration
  313                         | operator_declaration
  314                         | constructor_declaration
  315                         | finalizer_declaration
  316                         | static_constructor_declaration
  317                         | type_declaration

  318 constant_declaration: attributesopt modifiers_opt CONST type 
                                constant_declarators ';'

  319 constant_declarators: constant_declarator
  320                     | constant_declarators ',' constant_declarator

  321 constant_declarator: IDENTIFIER '=' constant_expression

  322 field_declaration: attributesopt modifiers_opt type 
                             variable_declarators ';'

  323 variable_declarators: variable_declarator
  324                     | variable_declarators ',' variable_declarator

  325 variable_declarator: IDENTIFIER
  326                    | IDENTIFIER '=' variable_initializer

  327 variable_initializer: expression
  328                     | array_initializer

  329 method_declaration: method_header method_body

  330 method_header: attributesopt modifiers_opt type member_name 
                         type_parameter_listopt '(' formal_parameter_listopt 
                         ')' type_parameter_constraints_clausesopt
  331              | attributesopt modifiers_opt VOID member_name 
                         type_parameter_listopt '(' formal_parameter_listopt 
                         ')' type_parameter_constraints_clausesopt

  332 member_name: IDENTIFIER
  333            | type_name '.' IDENTIFIER

  334 method_body: block
  335            | ';'

  336 formal_parameter_list: fixed_parameters
  337                      | fixed_parameters ',' parameter_array
  338                      | parameter_array

  339 fixed_parameters: fixed_parameter
  340                 | fixed_parameters ',' fixed_parameter

  341 fixed_parameter: attributesopt parameter_modifieropt type IDENTIFIER

  342 parameter_modifier: REF
  343                   | OUT

  344 parameter_array: attributesopt PARAMS array_type IDENTIFIER

  345 property_declaration: attributesopt modifiers_opt type member_name 
                                '{' accessor_declarations '}'

  346 accessor_declarations: get_accessor_declaration 
                                 set_accessor_declarationopt
  347                      | set_accessor_declaration 
                                 get_accessor_declarationopt

  348 get_accessor_declaration: attributesopt accessor_modifieropt GET 
                                    accessor_body

  349 set_accessor_declaration: attributesopt accessor_modifieropt SET 
                                    accessor_body

  350 accessor_modifier: PROTECTED
  351                  | INTERNAL
  352                  | PRIVATE
  353                  | PROTECTED INTERNAL
  354                  | INTERNAL PROTECTED

  355 accessor_body: block
  356              | ';'

  357 event_declaration: attributesopt modifiers_opt EVENT type 
                             variable_declarators ';'
  358                  | attributesopt modifiers_opt EVENT type member_name 
                             '{' event_accessor_declarations '}'

  359 event_accessor_declarations: add_accessor_declaration 
                                       remove_accessor_declaration
  360                            | remove_accessor_declaration 
                                       add_accessor_declaration

  361 add_accessor_declaration: attributesopt ADD block

  362 remove_accessor_declaration: attributesopt REMOVE block

  363 indexer_declaration: attributesopt modifiers_opt indexer_declarator 
                               '{' accessor_declarations '}'

  364 indexer_declarator: type THIS '[' formal_parameter_list ']'
  365                   | type type_name '.' THIS '[' formal_parameter_list 
                              ']'

  366 operator_declaration: attributesopt modifiers_opt operator_declarator 
                                operator_body

  367 operator_declarator: unary_operator_declarator
  368                    | binary_operator_declarator
  369                    | conversion_operator_declarator

  370 unary_operator_declarator: type OPERATOR overloadable_unary_operator 
                                     '(' type IDENTIFIER ')'

  371 overloadable_unary_operator: '+'
  372                            | '-'
  373                            | '!'
  374                            | '~'
  375                            | PLUS_PLUS
  376                            | MINUS_MINUS
  377                            | TRUE
  378                            | FALSE

  379 binary_operator_declarator: type OPERATOR 
                                      overloadable_binary_operator '(' type 
                                      IDENTIFIER ',' type IDENTIFIER ')'

  380 overloadable_binary_operator: '+'
  381                             | '-'
  382                             | '*'
  383                             | '/'
  384                             | '%'
  385                             | '&'
  386                             | '|'
  387                             | '^'
  388                             | LT_LT
  389                             | RIGHT_SHIFT
  390                             | EQ_EQ
  391                             | NE
  392                             | '>'
  393                             | '<'
  394                             | GE
  395                             | LE

  396 conversion_operator_declarator: IMPLICIT OPERATOR type '(' type 
                                          IDENTIFIER ')'
  397                               | EXPLICIT OPERATOR type '(' type 
                                          IDENTIFIER ')'

  398 operator_body: block
  399              | ';'

  400 constructor_declaration: attributesopt modifiers_opt 
                                   constructor_declarator constructor_body

  401 constructor_declarator: IDENTIFIER '(' formal_parameter_listopt ')' 
                                  constructor_initializeropt

  402 constructor_initializer: ':' BASE '(' argument_listopt ')'
  403                        | ':' THIS '(' argument_listopt ')'

  404 constructor_body: block
  405                 | ';'

  406 static_constructor_declaration: attributesopt modifiers_opt 
                                          IDENTIFIER '(' ')' 
                                          static_constructor_body

  407 static_constructor_body: block
  408                        | ';'

  409 finalizer_declaration: attributesopt modifiers_opt '~' IDENTIFIER '(' 
                                 ')' finalizer_body

  410 finalizer_body: block
  411               | ';'

  412 struct_declaration: attributesopt modifiers_opt STRUCT IDENTIFIER 
                              type_parameter_listopt struct_interfacesopt 
                              type_parameter_constraints_clausesopt 
                              struct_body SemicolonOpt

  413 struct_interfaces: type_name_list

  414 struct_body: '{' struct_member_declarationsopt '}'

  415 struct_member_declarations: struct_member_declaration
  416                           | struct_member_declarations

  418                          | field_declaration

  420                          | property_declaration
  421                          | event_declaration
  422                          | indexer_declaration
  423                          | operator_declaration
  424                          | constructor_declaration
  425                          | static_constructor_declaration
  426                          | type_declaration

  427 array_type: non_array_type rank_specifiers

  428 non_array_type: value_type
  429               | class_type

  430 rank_specifiers: rank_specifier
  431                | rank_specifiers rank_specifier

  432 rank_specifier: '[' dim_separatorsopt ']'

  433 dim_separators: ','
  434               | dim_separators ','

  435 array_initializer: '{' variable_initializer_listopt '}'
  436                  | '{' variable_initializer_list ',' '}'

  437 variable_initializer_list: variable_initializer
  438                          | variable_initializer_list ','

  439 interface_declaration: attributesopt modifiers_opt INTERFACE 
                                 IDENTIFIER type_parameter_listopt 
                                 interface_baseopt 
                                 type_parameter_constraints_clausesopt 
                                 interface_body SemicolonOpt

  440 interface_base: type_name_list

  441 interface_body: '{' interface_member_declarationsopt '}'

  442 interface_member_declarations: interface_member_declaration
  443                              | interface_member_declarations 
                                         interface_member_declaration

  444 interface_member_declaration: interface_method_declaration
  445                             | interface_property_declaration
  446                             | interface_event_declaration
  447                             | interface_indexer_declaration

  448 interface_method_declaration: attributesopt newopt type IDENTIFIER 
                                        type_parameter_listopt '(' 
                                        formal_parameter_listopt ')' 
                                        type_parameter_constraints_clausesopt 
                                        ';'
  449                             | attributesopt newopt VOID IDENTIFIER 
                                        type_parameter_listopt '(' 
                                        formal_parameter_listopt ')' 
                                        type_parameter_constraints_clausesopt 
                                        ';'

  450 interface_property_declaration: attributesopt newopt type IDENTIFIER 
                                          '{' interface_accessors '}'

  451 interface_accessors: attributesopt GET ';'
  452                    | attributesopt SET ';'
  453                    | attributesopt GET ';' attributesopt SET ';'
  454                    | attributesopt SET ';' attributesopt GET ';'

  455 interface_event_declaration: attributesopt newopt EVENT type 
                                       IDENTIFIER ';'

  456 interface_indexer_declaration: attributesopt newopt type THIS '[' 
                                         formal_parameter_list ']' '{' 
                                         interface_accessors '}'

  457 enum_declaration: attributesopt modifiers_opt ENUM IDENTIFIER 
                            enum_baseopt enum_body SemicolonOpt

  458 enum_base: ':' integral_type

  459 enum_body: '{' enum_member_declarationsopt '}'
  460          | '{' enum_member_declarations ',' '}'

  461 enum_member_declarations: enum_member_declaration
  462                         | enum_member_declarations ','

  463 enum_member_declaration: attributesopt IDENTIFIER

  465 delegate_declaration: attributesopt modifiers_opt DELEGATE type

  466                     | attributesopt modifiers_opt DELEGATE VOID 
                                IDENTIFIER type_parameter_listopt '(' 
                                formal_parameter_listopt ')' 
                                type_parameter_constraints_clausesopt ';'

  467 attributes: attribute_sections

  468 attribute_sections: attribute_section
  469                   | attribute_sections attribute_section

  470 attribute_section: '[' attribute_target_specifier attribute_list ']'
  471                  | '[' attribute_list ']'
  472                  | '[' attribute_target_specifier attribute_list ',' 
                             ']'
  473                  | '[' attribute_list ',' ']'

  474 attribute_target_specifier: attribute_target ':'

  475 attribute_target: IDENTIFIER
  476                 | keyword

  477 attribute_list: attribute
  478               | attribute_list ',' attribute

  479 attribute: attribute_name attribute_argumentsopt

  480 attribute_name: type_name

  481 attribute_arguments: '(' positional_argument_listopt ')'
  482                    | '(' positional_argument_list ',' 
                               named_argument_list ')'
  483                    | '(' named_argument_list ')'

  484 positional_argument_list: positional_argument
  485                         | positional_argument_list ',' 
                                    positional_argument

  486 positional_argument: attribute_argument_expression

  487 named_argument_list: named_argument
  488                    | named_argument_list ',' named_argument

  489 named_argument: IDENTIFIER '=' attribute_argument_expression

  490 attribute_argument_expression: expression

  491 type_parameter_list: '<' type_parameters '>'

  492 type_parameters: attributesopt IDENTIFIER
  493                | type_parameters ',' attributesopt IDENTIFIER

  494 type_argument_list: '<' type_arguments '>'

  495 type_arguments: type_argument
  496               | type_arguments ',' type_argument

  497 type_argument: type

  498 type_parameter_constraints_clauses: type_parameter_constraints_clause
  499                                   | 
                                              type_parameter_constraints_clauses 
                                              type_parameter_constraints_clause

  500 type_parameter_constraints_clause: WHERE IDENTIFIER ':' 
                                             type_parameter_constraints

  501 type_parameter_constraints: primary_constraint
  502                           | secondary_constraints
  503                           | constructor_constraint
  504                           | primary_constraint ',' 
                                      secondary_constraints
  505                           | primary_constraint ',' 
                                      constructor_constraint
  506                           | secondary_constraints ',' 
                                      constructor_constraint
  507                           | primary_constraint ',' 
                                      secondary_constraints ',' 
                                      constructor_constraint

  508 primary_constraint: class_type
  509                   | CLASS
  510                   | STRUCT

  511 secondary_constraints: type_name
  512                      | secondary_constraints ',' type_name

  513 constructor_constraint: NEW '(' ')'

  514 keyword: ABSTRACT
  515        | AS
  516        | BASE
  517        | BOOL
  518        | BREAK
  519        | CASE
  520        | CATCH
  521        | CHECKED
  522        | CLASS
  523        | CONST
  524        | CONTINUE
  525        | DECIMAL
  526        | DEFAULT
  527        | DELEGATE
  528        | DO
  529        | DOUBLE
